Police have arrested a man who has been on the run after conning several M-Pesa agents of thousands of shillings. The man was arrested by officers from the Directorate of Criminal Investigations at his house at Mwanzo Estate on Saturday morning following a tip-off from the public. Eldoret West DCIO Aden Guyo said the man was arrested following complaints from several M-Pesa operators. He is alleged to have also robbed an M-Pesa agent along the Eldoret-Webuye road of more than Sh58, 000. &nbsp;